  <brief_title>Effect of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Children Undergoing Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Remote Ischemic Preconditioning on Children Undergoing Cardiac Surgery: Implication of Preoperative Cyanosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
